said.
 

00:12:46.769 --> 00:12:48.750
What did someone say,
something that would have--

00:12:48.750 --> 00:12:52.583
it wasn't the--is the one child
policy happened at this time but

00:12:52.583 --> 00:12:55.080
something else happened in both
India,

00:12:55.080 --> 00:12:58.058
and China, and Korea.
 

