It costs I think about $14 in
India, in this period of time,

00:13:38.705 --> 00:13:43.808
to get an ultrasound test of
what your fetus was.

00:13:43.808 --> 00:13:49.490
In one of the counties in
China, for instance,

00:13:49.490 --> 00:13:53.610
they started doing ultrasound,
and what happened was the first

00:13:53.610 --> 00:13:55.866
child,
and I'll show you some data,

